featured_reviews.review_id:
Musafir khana is conduct by Anjuman islahul muslemeen Masjid, Ratlam located at mhow nimuch road near underbridge.

Musafir khana is the place, where every person can stay here with just little cost. Many travelers, workers from other cities staying here and like for reasonable cost and facilities.

It is located near few distance from Railway station and bus stand and market area.

Restaurant for veg and non-veg are also available below this building. Public transport like taxi auto are available near just some meters distance.
